- **Type of Buy-back:** On-market buy-back.  
- **Total Buy-back Program:** Up to **$750 million** of ordinary shares (ALL).  
- **Daily Buy-back Activity (22/7/2025):**

  - **Total Bought to Date:** 3,300,695.  
  - **Daily Consideration:** AUD 5.80 million (avg. ~AUD 67.40/share).  
- **Price Range (Previous Day):** AUD 67.05 (low) to AUD 67.80 (high).  
- **Program Period:** 7/3/2025 to 6/3/2026.
